data.description: PRICE REDUCED! SELLER WILL CREDIT $10,000 TOWARD BUYER CLOSING COSTS! POOL & SPA! PAID OFF SOLAR! Spacious South Temecula pool home with 5 bdrms + loft, 3 baths. Open floorplan with huge Great Room, open kitchen with large island and breakfast bar, walk-in pantry, double ovens, built-in gas cooktop, soft-close drawers, all SS appliances. Full bed and bath downstairs. The first floor was built to ADA guidelines, including roll-in shower, wide doorways and halls, and exterior hardscaping has easy access in and out of the home. All ADA modifications were done by the builder (Lennar Homes) at the time of construction. Outdoor "California Room" with fireplace, beautiful Saltwater pool & spa with "beach style" entry and flagstone accents, and 2 grassy lawn areas. Upstairs has NEW CARPET, a huge loft, the Primary Suite + Retreat, large ensuite bath with dual sinks, vanity area, separate tub and shower, and huge walk-in closet. Upstairs laundry room with tons of storage, 3 additional upstairs bedrooms, a Hall Bath with dual sinks & separated shower area. Total of 5 bedrooms, plus the retreat, plus the loft, plus a Flex Room near the front entry door which can be used as a Formal Living Room, Office, or Den. 3-car tandem garage, paid off solar, tankless water heater, whole house fan, dual AC. Terracina Community, Great Oak High School District.
